and  linked  challenges  in  tackling  climate  change,  promoting  clean 
energy and achieving sustainable development globally.’’ 

The  G8  leaders  agreed  that  the  Gleneagles  Program  of  Action,  a 
broad-based  practical  program  of  over  50  activities  to  address  cli-
mate change, to secure clean and affordable sources of energy, and 
to  promote  sustainable  development  over  the  coming  decades.  The 

