Senator  LAUTENBERG.  Forecast  about  flooded  nations,  I  mean, 
you know, if we look at recent history and October 2003, the Ward 
Hunt  Ice  Shelf,  the  largest  ice  shelf  in  the  Antarctic  broke  up.  I 
